label.value: kidney loop of Henle descending limb epithelial cell

value.value: Any kidney loop of Henle epithelial cell that is part of some descending limb of loop of Henle.

An endothelial cell that is part of the peritubular capillary of the kidney. This cell is highly fenestrated and plays a vital role in the kidney's filtration process, enabling the exchange of materials between the blood and the renal tubules.
Peritubular capillary endothelial cells feature fenestrations measuring 60-70 nm in diameter, each traversed by a thin diaphragm.
A cell that is part of a vasa recta.
Any kidney arterial blood vessel cell that is part of some renal cortex artery.
Any kidney venous blood vessel cell that is part of some renal cortex vein.

definition.value: Note that the source of this term is KUPO:0001096 (artery smooth muscle cell), which we believe actually denotes the kidney specific structure.
Note that the source of this term is KUPO:0001098 (arteriole smooth muscle cell), which we believe actually denotes the kidney specific structure.

label.value: kidney venous system smooth muscle cell

definition.value: Note that the source of this term is KUPO:0001068 (venous system smooth muscle cell), which we believe actually denotes the kidney specific structure.

value.value: An endothelial cell that lines the interior surface of the afferent arteriole and maintains vascular tone. This cell responds to changing ion concentrations and blood pressure by releasing vasoactive substances, in order to regulate blood flow into the glomeruli, which is essential for glomerular filtration.

label.value: kidney afferent arteriole smooth muscle cell

value.value: A smooth muscle cell found in the wall of the afferent arteriole. This cell contracts and relaxes in response to changes in blood pressure, a process known as a myogenic response, to alter artery diameter and regulate blood flow into the glomeruli.
Any endothelial cell that is part of some renal efferent arteriole.

label.value: kidney efferent arteriole smooth muscle cell

value.value: Any smooth muscle cell that is part of some renal efferent arteriole.

label.value: kidney loop of Henle thick ascending limb epithelial cell

value.value: An epithelial cell that is part of some loop of Henle thick ascending limb. It is known in some mammalian species that this cell may express the Na+-K+-2Clcotransporter (NKCC2) apically.

label.value: kidney loop of Henle thin ascending limb epithelial cell

definition.value: An epithelial cell that is part of some loop of Henle thin ascending limb.

label.value: kidney loop of Henle medullary thick ascending limb epithelial cell

definition.value: An epithelial cell that is part of some loop of Henle thick ascending limb segment located in the renal medulla.

label.value: kidney loop of Henle cortical thick ascending limb epithelial cell

definition.value: An epithelial cell that is part of some loop of Henle thick ascending limb segment located in the renal cortex.

label.value: kidney loop of Henle thin descending limb epithelial cell

definition.value: An epithelial cell that is part of some loop of Henle thin descending limb.

label.value: kidney outer medulla peritubular capillary cell

definition.value: An endothelial cell that is part of the peritubular capillary of the outer renal medulla.
An endothelial cell that is part of the peritubular capillary of the renal cortex.

label.value: inner renal medulla vasa recta cell

value.value: Any vasa recta cell that is part of some inner renal medulla vasa recta.

label.value: outer renal medulla vasa recta cell

value.value: Any vasa recta cell that is part of some outer renal medulla vasa recta.

definition.value: A cell that is part of some vasa recta ascending limb.

value.value: It is known in some mammalian species that this cell may express PV-1, a component of the fenestral diaphragm.
Any kidney cortex artery cell that is part of some kidney arcuate artery.
Any kidney cortex artery cell that is part of some interlobular artery.
Any kidney cortex vein cell that is part of some kidney arcuate vein.
Any kidney cortex vein cell that is part of some renal interlobular vein.

label.value: inner medulla vasa recta ascending limb cell

value.value: Any vasa recta ascending limb cell that is part of some inner medulla vasa recta ascending limb.

label.value: outer medulla vasa recta ascending limb cell

value.value: Any vasa recta ascending limb cell that is part of some outer medulla vasa recta ascending limb.
Any endothelial cell that is part of some kidney arcuate artery.
Any smooth muscle cell that is part of some kidney arcuate artery.
Any endothelial cell that is part of some interlobular artery.
Any smooth muscle cell that is part of some interlobular artery.
Any endothelial cell that is part of some kidney arcuate vein.
Any smooth muscle cell that is part of some kidney arcuate vein.
Any endothelial cell that is part of some renal interlobular vein.
Any smooth muscle cell that is part of some renal interlobular vein.

definition.value: A cell that is part of a collecting duct of renal tubule.
A cell that is part of some vasa recta descending limb.

value.value: It is known in some mammalian species that this cell may express the urea transporter B.

label.value: inner medulla vasa recta descending limb cell

value.value: Any vasa recta descending limb cell that is part of some inner medulla vasa recta descending limb.

label.value: outer medulla vasa recta descending limb cell

value.value: Any vasa recta descending limb cell that is part of some outer medulla vasa recta descending limb.

definition.value: A pericyte cell located in the kidney interstitium.

value.value: Any cell that is part of some urinary bladder.
Any cell that is part of some urethra.
A urothelial cell that is part of the urothelium of the urinary bladder.
Any urothelial cell that is part of some urethra urothelium.
Any renal principal cell that is part of some collecting duct of renal tubule.
An epithelial cell of the exocrine pancreas.
A neuron residing in the olfactory bulb that serve to process and refine signals arising from olfactory sensory neurons

label.value: sensory neuron of dorsal root ganglion

value.value: A sensory neuron of the dorsal root ganglia that senses body position and sends information about how much the muscle is stretched to the spinal cord.

The large glutaminergic nerve cells whose dendrites synapse with axons of the olfactory receptor neurons in the glomerular layer of the olfactory bulb, and whose axons pass centrally in the olfactory tract to the olfactory cortex.
